Say FizzBuzz from 1 to 20.
Let i be 1.
While i <= 20 do the following.
  If i % 15 = 0 then do the following.
    Say FizzBuzz.
  Otherwise do the following.
    If i % 3 = 0 then do the following.
      Say Fizz.
    Otherwise do the following.
      If i % 5 = 0 then do the following.
        Say Buzz.
      Otherwise do the following.
        Display i.
      End if.
    End if.
  End if.
  Let i be i + 1.
End while.

Note: Countdown with Stop when we hit 3.
Say counting down with stop at 3.
Let n be 10.
While n > 0 do the following.
  If n = 3 then do the following.
    Say stopping at 3.
    Stop.
  End if.
  Display n.
  Let n be n - 1.
End while.
